 *
 * 1. Parses Forgejo push webhook payload for changed .md files
 * 2. Filters excluded paths (system/, private, assets, .obsidian/)
 * 3. Loop prevention: skips commits from n8n/vault-embedding authors
 * 4. Reads files from /vault/, computes SHA256, parses YAML frontmatter
 * 5. Chunks content by ## headings with paragraph-boundary splitting
 * 6. Calls TEI embedding API via wget/spawn for each chunk batch
 * 7. Builds pre-formatted SQL (DELETE old + INSERT new) for each file
 * 8. Outputs items with {query} for the PostgreSQL Execute node
 * 9. Final item has {_isSummary: true} for the response branch
 *
